    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Divo Augusto <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uintus</ex></expan> Fabius <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uinti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> Varus <expan><abbr>pontif</abbr><ex>ex</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>Vvir <note>sic</note> cryptam hypaetrum <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>e</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ua</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ecunia</ex></expan> <supplied reason="lost" cert="low">d(edit)</supplied> dedicavit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Y: Datierung ab 17.9.14 (consecratio des Augustus). Z. 3: Vvir verschrieben für IVvir. Abweichende Deutungen von hypaetrum: als ambulationes hypaetrae (Puertas Tricas) - als Temenos für städtischen Kaisertempel (Etienne).</p>
            </div>
